OL,3,CCross-border tourism has tripled in a
OL,4,Cdecade ` all-island report
OL,6,FInternational visits in the period
OL,7,F2013-2019 grew by 33% in Northern
OL,8,FIreland and 46% south of the border.
OL,10,FThe authors said that "notwithstanding
OL,11,Fsome public commentary that many
OL,12,Fpeople from the Republic of Ireland
OL,13,Fnever travel to NI", the number of
OL,14,Ftrips from south of the border to
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland has "increased
OL,16,Fdramatically" over the past decade.
