OL,3,CCross-border tourism has tripled in a
OL,4,Cdecade ` all-island report
OL,6,FAna Desmond, senior economist at the
OL,7,FUlster University Economic Policy
OL,8,FCentre, said the tourism sector across
OL,9,Fthe island of Ireland "has
OL,10,Fdemonstrated remarkable growth and
OL,11,Fresilience" in recent years.
OL,13,F"This research has shown how the
OL,14,Finternational and domestic visitor
OL,15,Fmarket has both grown and diversified
OL,16,Fwith recent significant findings
OL,17,Fincluding the sharp and sustained
OL,18,Fincrease in domestic cross-border
OL,19,Fvisits to NI since the Covid-19
OL,20,Fpandemic.
